The tags are the names given to the separate areas of the text.
The tags are used to configure the different areas of the text separately.




SN	                       Method	                                             Description

1	         tag_add(tagname, startindex, endindex)	               This method is used to tag the string
                                                                   present in the specified range.



2	                     tag_config	                               This method is used to configure the
                                                                   tag properties.



3	                tag_delete(tagname)	                           This method is used to delete a given
                                                                   tag.



4	        tag_remove(tagname, startindex, endindex)	           This method is used to remove a tag from
                                                                   the specified range.